<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1035 gunēṁṭi cai
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tra sudha Ēkadaśi ravivā<supplied reason="omitted">ra</supplied>munāṁḍu varaṇasi
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kaṭakana siriyamudasiri tanaku Abhīṣṭarta
<lb n="4" break="no"/>sidhigānu <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīnarasiṁhyanāthuniki nityamunnu
<lb n="5"/>Ubhayadupālaṁdu parimāṟānu Oka ve<unclear>ṁ</unclear>
<lb n="6" break="no"/>jāmaramu samarppiṁciri I kolupu koluva
<lb n="7" break="no"/>nu gaṁgabhōgena tara<unclear>sa</unclear>ni kuturu pōlamaku pe
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṭenu Iṁdulaku śrībhaṁḍaramaṁdu padmani<supplied reason="omitted">dhi</supplied>mala
<lb n="9" break="no"/>lu māḍalu 3 samarpiṁci kuṁca prasādamu vṛtti
<lb n="10" break="no"/>gā koni peṭenu I prasādamu bujiṁci cāmarakolu
<lb n="11" break="no"/>pu Ācaṁdrarka<unclear>stā</unclear>Igā koluvaṁga<supplied reason="omitted">la</supplied>du nibaṁda sama
